## SEO Agency in Berkshire or SEO Company in Berkshire: What You Actually Get

Searching for an "SEO agency in Berkshire" or an "SEO company in Berkshire"? Here's the honest answer: I'm not an agency. I'm an independent consultant, and that's a deliberate structural choice, not a smaller version of the same thing.

A Berkshire SEO agency puts an account manager between you and the person doing the strategy work, and that layer is funded from your monthly fee. Working with me, you get the same scope an agency sells, technical audits, local SEO, topical authority content, reporting, delivered directly by the senior strategist, with no juniors and no account management overhead. The trade-off is capacity: agencies can staff up for very high-volume production; I can't. For most Berkshire businesses, direct senior access outperforms that trade-off.

